            "title": "中環住宅大廈5條銅管被盜 裝修工人揭發報警求助",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"探員到場調查銅管被盜事件。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/552707e6dfb7102c1364a8c8b3abd88d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031215421791923.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">探員到場調查銅管被盜事件。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中環卑利街66號，今（12日）中午1時44分，警方接報指該大廈後巷被偷走多條銅喉，警員到場調查，據悉，昨早裝修工人已經發現有銅喉不翼而飛，今早通知判頭，負責人獲悉事件後決定報警求助，經點算後， 近後巷位置被偷走共5條銅管，警方將案件列盜竊案處理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133030/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大廈後巷位置被盜去5條銅喉。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a09c67f3799d2ef23ec942c07121f438/2025-03/1_1_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大廈後巷位置被盜去5條銅喉。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133031/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c8fa8c55c2a4cd436e59a407b410e9ba/2025-03/2_2_48.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4133032/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"探員到場調查。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/78c0a2453faa340631685cf1abf17b88/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_151136479_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        探員到場調查。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
