        {
            "title": "販毒集團招攬親友「家庭式」營運 警拘4男女包括母女 檢$1400萬貨",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"毒品調查科督察吳嘉煒展示證物。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/eecf679f887f4ad66834f0638d0149f7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031215145377228.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">毒品調查科督察吳嘉煒展示證物。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>警方發現有販毒集團招攬親朋戚友，由入貨、分拆至銷售，以家庭式「一條龍」營運。毒品調查科人員於前日（10日）採取行動，拘捕集團主腦及骨幹成員在內的4名越南籍男女，其中兩名女子更屬母女關係，共檢獲約24公斤的海洛英、氯胺酮、冰毒、大麻花及搖頭丸，市值超過1,400萬元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132928/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方檢獲大批毒品。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c868976e9dc7d8458d2e94b3136f9a3e/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方檢獲大批毒品。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132929/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉案的毒品證物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/561890f72dd9cb8cafd83849f0cc36e6/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉案的毒品證物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132930/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c885bcbf945eefeac918d2157aee0676/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132931/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57e84164b0fac464bc7f2fc108495576/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132932/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a79e2dea0f49aeb2c19d1edbbf8e20b2/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>被捕4名越南籍男女，年齡介乎31至64歲，全部報稱無業；當中一人是非法入境，而另外三人則持「行街紙」。他們分別涉嫌「串謀販運危險藥物」、「販運危險藥物」、「阻礙公職人員執行公務」及「非法入境」。\n\n</p>\n<p>初步調查顯示，涉案集團所有成員都互相認識，當中被捕的兩名女子屬母女關係。警方相信有人為減低被揭發的風險，從親朋戚友入手，招攬他們成為販毒集團一份子，以「一條龍」販毒模式，分別負責入貨、倉管、分拆及銷售毒品的角色。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132933/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ae1567b3939dd6406fd851ec5cd282a9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132934/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba79fd2492a52d1d170fc90a3ced6775/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132935/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6eea6a9f1df75946f2d3639b88b2b0dc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132936/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/73f4b8787a1d54599aa2aff0e017ffb8/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132937/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c8518f2c7c46357ee72dede37acf9c1d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>前日毒品調查科探員在旺角染布房街一幢大廈，截查兩名形迹可疑的女子，分別在她們手持的一個袋和身上的斜孭袋內，檢獲20磚共重7公斤的海洛英，以及一包約200克重的氯胺酮。人員隨即將兩名女子拘捕，其後將她們押返附近一個劏房單位作搜查，並在劏房內發現另一名外籍男子，其間該名男子一度反抗，最後被制服。人員在單位內再檢獲約5.9公斤海洛英、8.5公斤氯胺酮、1.7公斤冰毒、約2,500粒搖頭丸，以及 130克大麻花。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132938/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7dae319bbfb84c54fefe64f2bf51ec1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132939/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/237fed75c17fb08279aee945cfcfe089/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132940/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a4a4f597f312b507cedac01a326a5d9/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132941/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f87ac8f16171153f20786fa94bf664f7/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141414957_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132947/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"毒品調查科督察吳嘉煒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99d706f30e6762792f6f5c8d781aa0db/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141219751.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        毒品調查科督察吳嘉煒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132948/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6ecf67065c5167a928b27c1494223db/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_141219751_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>探員進行深入調查，於旺角另一私人住宅內拘捕另一名與案有關男子，該名男子在警方調查過程中，同樣作出反抗，最後被探員制服。人在其住所檢獲約203克嘅冰毒和約24克氯胺酮。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方相信今次行動已成功瓦解一個家庭式販毒集團，並且拘捕了集團的主腦及骨幹成員。4名被捕人正被扣留調查，稍後將被起訴，案件將於明日（13日）在西九龍裁判法院提堂。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057715/即時-港聞-販毒集團招攬親友-家庭式-營運-警拘4男女包括母女-檢-1400萬貨",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-12 15:21:42",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "4歲男童焦急報警「快來抓我媽」 母自首：我吃了他的雪糕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"美國男童因為雪糕被媽媽吃掉，焦急報警「抓媽媽」。  facebook / Village Of Mount Pleasant Police Department\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/96c4f5fbb5c8316b980f2861909edacd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031215155435159.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">美國男童因為雪糕被媽媽吃掉，焦急報警「抓媽媽」。  facebook / Village Of Mount Pleasant Police Department</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國威斯康辛州發生一宗搞笑「雪糕失竊案」，一名4歲男童打911報警，表示「我的媽媽很壞」、她「必須進監獄」，結果媽媽發現他在報警後插嘴，自首說「因為我吃他的雪糕」。警方擔心有隱情，仍派員到場查看，隔天再上門請男孩吃雪糕，藉機教育他緊急情況才使用911服務。\n\n</p><h2>「必須進監獄！」</h2>\n<p>芒特普萊森特鎮（Mount Pleasant）警方日前在facebook發文稱，事發於3月4日，「一名小男孩撥打911說，他的媽媽很壞，必須進監獄」。警察趕到家中時，孩子說，「媽媽吃了他的雪糕，必須為此進監獄」。不過後來男孩反悔，表示「不想讓她進監獄了，只是想要回雪糕。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"小鎮警方分享這宗搞笑「雪糕失竊案」。 facebook截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/47ff3413d42aab62d3102d8aa540a6e6/2025-03/2025-03-12_150618.JPEG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        小鎮警方分享這宗搞笑「雪糕失竊案」。 facebook截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>美媒取得這段求助電話的錄音，顯示電話中有女子聲音說明：「我吃了他的雪糕，這可能是他致電911的原因。」警員擔心有隱情，仍派員上門查看，釐清狀況之後不禁莞爾，隨即離開。隔天警員再上門，買了兩份雪糕給男童和他的妹妹，以獎勵他「不再希望媽媽惹上麻煩」。\n\n</p>\n<p>網民議論紛紛，有人嚴肅表示「你獎勵了一個孩子的罪行。」「這不行，需要儘早教導孩子撥打 911 的適當時間。」也有人寫道：「我不是要說他是對的，我只是想說，我能理解他的心情。」「至少他知道如何呼救。」「我好喜歡聽見我們出色的警察與孩子建立積極關係。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057716/即時-國際-4歲男童焦急報警-快來抓我媽-母自首-我吃了他的雪糕",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-12 15:21:43",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "6旬男行小馬山暈倒受傷 直升機救起送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"行山男子受傷送院。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/16b6df30a55266758c99ddc0dcc51128/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031215064642465.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">行山男子受傷送院。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>港島畢拉山道小馬山，今（12日）中午1時27分，一名年約60歲男子被發現倒臥在往小馬山的石橋上，身體擦傷流血，行山人士報警求助，政府飛行服務隊出動直升機，將男事主救起，他仍然清醒，被送往東區醫院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132943/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事主由直升機救起送東區醫院治理。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fe4da79263c8767345747aa60612f891/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_143420711_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事主由直升機救起送東區醫院治理。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132944/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事主獲救時清醒。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a783496ea1b2726bfc0877a9c948c999/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_143420711_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事主獲救時清醒。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132945/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7baf9da6f0c3472a182ce4fa6813b741/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_143420711_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132946/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d50dccf2f5f83e498f012cb7288fab38/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_144249899.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4132942/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"事主由直升機救起送院。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14e0d4a2f18eaafb3b772cc7bf2009b4/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_143420711.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事主由直升機救起送院。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
