        {
            "title": "天氣︱冷鋒周六殺到一晚跌10度 周日市區最低僅15°C 下周初乾燥最低濕度35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"天氣︱冷鋒周六晚殺到 周日一夜跌10度 市區最低僅15°C 內陸地區有雷暴\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8f958b55ae905775d455c15d8a056d50/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250312/_2025031215045346802.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">天氣︱冷鋒周六晚殺到 周日一夜跌10度 市區最低僅15°C 內陸地區有雷暴</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【天氣/天文台/乾燥/潮濕/冷鋒】天文台預料，一股潮濕的偏東氣流會在明日（13日）逐漸影響華南沿岸，廣東沿岸風勢微弱。同時，一道廣闊雲帶覆蓋該區。本港方面，今早新界東、九龍及大嶼山錄得數毫米雨量。未來兩三日該區有幾陣霧。\n\n</p><h2>下周初至中期天色漸好轉 天氣乾燥</h2>\n<p>天文台指，一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）晚上至周日（16日）橫過沿岸地區並為該區帶來幾陣驟雨，而內陸地區有雷暴。受隨後的東北季候風影響，周日沿岸地區天氣轉涼，下周初至中期天色逐漸好轉，天氣乾燥，早晚清涼。\n\n</p>\n<p>據九天天氣預測，周六（15日）最高氣溫達25度，但晚上冷鋒「殺到」，一晚急跌10度，周日（16日）市區最低只有15度。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"天文台預料，一股潮濕的偏東氣流會在明日（13日）逐漸影響華南沿岸。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4fbaebb50a17ca5c262fbb532bbfa3b/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_093701357_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        天文台預料，一股潮濕的偏東氣流會在明日（13日）逐漸影響華南沿岸。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"同時，一道廣闊雲帶覆蓋該區。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e794f95351728954b6375eaf8097329/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_093701357_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        同時，一道廣闊雲帶覆蓋該區。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今早新界東、九龍及大嶼山錄得數毫米雨量。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ed789a2c53187c1b6458090f6eaf37af/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_093701357_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今早新界東、九龍及大嶼山錄得數毫米雨量。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）晚上至周日（16日）橫過沿岸地區並為該區帶來幾陣驟雨。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4be59c54bc456bb2e3cd61e5c98ab6be/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_093701357_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一道冷鋒會在周六（15日）晚上至周日（16日）橫過沿岸地區並為該區帶來幾陣驟雨。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"下周初至中期天色逐漸好轉，天氣乾燥，早晚清涼。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d853858649b4251a9c7b58f5e67d09c/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250312_093701357_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        下周初至中期天色逐漸好轉，天氣乾燥，早晚清涼。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預測。天文台網站截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3226e66e85a9d7b31bfca5359ead8336/2025-03/2025-03-12_145636.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預測。天文台網站截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"早晚有一兩陣微雨。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f6bab7bb62de00002358b3a1fcb5841/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-12-06-45-35_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        早晚有一兩陣微雨。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"日間短暫時間有陽光及相當溫暖。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6462d68f9df8943fa927fe8e7d5f1211/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-12-06-45-38_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間短暫時間有陽光及相當溫暖。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"最高氣溫約26度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1ac4916b5a2fe8af3176307cd3667ae/2025-03/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-03-12-06-45-41_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        最高氣溫約26度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>本港地區下午及今晚天氣預測大致多雲，有一兩陣雨及薄霧。下午部分時間天色明朗。吹微風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望未來一兩日天氣潮濕，沿岸有霧。明日日間溫暖。星期六晚上至星期日北風增強，氣溫逐步下降。下週初天氣乾燥，早晚清涼。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
